Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我和阿三哥在一起之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会变得成熟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一道曙光！看不到第一道曙光！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明等了这么久！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 阿柳 打草惊蛇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是那个吗 那道曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在那座建筑物的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:39.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说看见太阳的时候不就是新年的日出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:43.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地平线出现的时候才是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同学 你也太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 因为不好好定义的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:51.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知道今年的第一次日出是看到还是没看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫做第一次日出 也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但说到底 地平线也看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么妥协方式让人这么不痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫　不要在意这些小事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是我们等的新年日出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大楼日出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说新年日出了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能日出我也还是第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:21.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我的话不管怎样每年都有看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:22.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么一说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还真没看过 日出什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:26.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有看过日出的人还蛮多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:34.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 夏目他们也许也没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了不能和大家一起疯的年纪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳比我想象的还要大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:51.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:54.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:57.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,些微小事我都会觉得超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年的时候能再和大家一起来看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.00,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs140\c&H0000AF&\frz18.12\pos(240,171)}春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.00,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(315,259)}天\N将至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,热闹的新年结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于回到了平静的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和弟弟两人都在奶奶家里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这个更好的学习环境了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:04.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想安心下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,元旦以后就没有见过春了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不在意的话 那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在春他在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻听了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫 在的话就快点回答啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是怎么了 春？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:45.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就稍微离开了会 就不知道跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 春 你先冷静下来慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这个还是保密中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是令人着急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:06.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫 抱歉 现在没有多余的时间陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 吃年糕会胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.77,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在急什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么 怎么了啊 穿成这个样子 春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有看见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:45.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一目了然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有空闲陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之发现了的话 就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你的博客一直都有错别字哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 网？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:08.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的内容我就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之发现了就告诉我吧 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒子要正确运用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个是荤段子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 水谷同学 怎么会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个电话是刚才春落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚吉田来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么他样子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.34,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像在找些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许对春来说是个大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一般人看来可能算不上严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边社团活动刚刚结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去把吉田落下的潜水镜送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同学打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:26.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 这不是又成长了一步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤疤是男人的勋章啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是阑尾炎 你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:35.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你口吐白沫的倒下 我都不知道怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到测量体温的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 让二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看望已经结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐测吧 是姐姐来测的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己进来喽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(550,147)}致春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(694,276)}我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(760,374)}晚上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(678,518)}自己随便吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我只是把春忘记的手机送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是刚刚遇见了春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像在找些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:35.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春同学的行为比以前还要难以理解 有一点担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿三哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好像出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,门没锁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:44.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是粗心大意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学还要留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是的 反正我也没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等春回来的时候帮我交给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:03.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在学习 而且还有想在今天做完的问题集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:08.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的寒假 当面给春比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他什么时候回来 留在这只会浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.65,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是个闲人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:18.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学 你遇到什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 什 什么事 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么事的话就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该没什么变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:38.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是发烧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是让二得阑尾炎的话不是很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们总是和他在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 我肚子也有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个彻底搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  没有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们几个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近有野猪 你们也小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人哪里好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学？怎么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚小水把手机送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白你的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学也来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 阿佐怎么也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田来社团的时候一副很慌乱的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也见到吉田了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在寻找些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了小水他还能找什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然本人说要学习就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们买点果汁什么的可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自动贩卖机的话没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能玩游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在别人家随便用电不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又不知道配电盘在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(302,408,302,670)\fs50\c&H302F2B&\3c&HFEFEFE&\fn方正大黑简体\pos(302,408)}我捡到了鸡~(·∑·)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(123,566,123,670)\fs50\c&H302F2B&\3c&HFEFEFE&\fn方正大黑简体\pos(123,566)}优
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小优？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你捡到的那只鸡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只鸡有名字什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 名古屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在路口是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,过路口之后的道路左边是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 小优同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 阿佐 我们几个先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 再见 我们再等一会吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来怎么还不回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早的联谊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 店不是打烊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们怎么来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:30.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是阿佐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:40.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 夏目同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么你们会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春那个笨蛋把这个落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们特意给送过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来吉田正为了找名古屋而到处徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田当时是什么样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身又湿又脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是寻找小鸡的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春同学现在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:16.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在超越人类想象的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到山里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:25.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要找到春田同学告诉他名古屋回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要去哪找他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 不要在意我 请继续讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他也许在河边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:41.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身湿透 捕鱼网
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我家的时候身上还沾着只长在河边的草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么要到那里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山贤 你要回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:06.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴才会陪你们一起找春 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 那我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:15.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊什么啊 明明是春同学的朋友 却这么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你们 我们几个去找就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小水？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 小夏目要去找吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是当然了 就算只剩下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦 山贤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶尔也应该有点人情味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那山贤同学补习班再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 我家从这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:08.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:16.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么山贤同学会走到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道 原因很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 山贤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大马路应该在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路的话 老老实实说出来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 反正大马路就在前面不远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要我帮你拿那袋米也行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我就拿了这点东西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里啊？快出来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人究竟是不是来找人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到晚上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同学 你先回棒球中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定吉田已经回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且店长说不定也已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人在会比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 我们继续找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经给春同学留了电话和纸条了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果他回来的话 会和我们联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想见他 可是没有见面的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 要一直走到河川的尽头哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,See You Again！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏目 不管你走到哪里我都会追随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了的话 我来背你o(*≧▽≦)ツ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 让二？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,让二的伤口裂开了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,让二 让二！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该问你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名古屋的话 我们已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在棒球中心那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:47.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名古屋？名古屋不见了吗？什么时候不见的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在找名古屋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 是虫子 会发光的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,发光的虫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上找到的 结果被它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处找了好久 可是哪都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大冬天里会发光的虫子 会不会是你看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 在发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,像萤火虫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫不会在冬天里出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别地漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想和雫一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:20.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你一起看的话 会变得更加更加地漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:29.34,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是大米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地适合你呢 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他可以看起来总是那么开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦这么想 就会觉得他有时遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还无法追赶上他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法从容地接受他的那种纯粹和直率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫！就是那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:15.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后查了下 说是南方有一种萤火虫能在冬天活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如春所说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不能确定是不是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着美丽的光芒滑过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失在了夜空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有许多不得不说的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于她的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于她的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:46.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于它的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(494,510,494,650)\fad(300,0)\fs50\c&H2F3433&\3c&HF3F5F5&\fn方正稚艺_GBK\frx32\fry0\pos(494,510)\frz358.7}您的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许总有一天我也能如此直率地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:22:00.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此坦诚地注视着身旁的他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:09.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 那道荧光确实看起来很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许 比起一个人看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:17.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要漂亮得太多…太多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:55.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 外面开始下雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:58.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好您好 晚上好o(*￣▽￣*)ゞ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:04.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…个 你是谁？
